data.subject: Alteration Of Capital and Fund Raising-XBRL

data.purpose: METROPOLIS HEALTHCARE LIMITED has informed the Exchange about Board Meeting to be held on 09-Dec-2024 to consider Fund raising.
To consider issuance of equity shares of the Company on a preferential basis

METROPOLIS HEALTHCARE LIMITED has informed the Exchange about Board Meeting to be held on 08-Nov-2024 to inter-alia consider and approve the Unaudited Financial results of the Company for the Quarterly ended September 2024 .
To consider and approve the financial results for the period ended September 30, 2024
To consider and approve the financial results for the period ended Jun 30, 2024
To consider and approve the Audited Standalone & Consolidated Financial Results for the period ended March 31, 2024
